{"tid":1787980,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"警告大家咪撚再講巴士","createTime":"2019-12-18T10:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T15:57:36.000Z","uid":38189,"like":21,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cb95fe6b5fbcf26d7cbd978bcb0ba15a371bcdaa","tid":1787980,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"見到你地係咁抽巴士水<br />\n我真係越諗越撚灰<br />\n根本唔知自己做乜要支持一種交通工具10幾年而換得俾人嘲笑既地步<br />\n知唔知咩叫尊重、respect?<br />\n好撚煩囉成日搬D歷史出o黎話點話點<br />\n我心諗一句, 你講既我全部知, 甚至乎你唔知既我都知<br />\n第一唔使你教我<br />\n第二唔使你分析我聽<br />\n第三我無屌你隊愛車先<br />\n一失分出面最少半版post 係抽水<br />\n好難忍到一個都唔reply<br />\n或者轉去其他forum 係唯一解決方法"},{"pid":"1c88386247f8abab11b27cceddb6b2ea6731e0ed","tid":1787980,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"你都唔係放開巴士"},{"pid":"e62b643a0dd394ebde818fe2bfdb1854eb9cbc1f","tid":1787980,"uid":581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"玩留"},{"pid":"fb6badbdf64615cde68cafe04bbde3fce5729f4f","tid":1787980,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1c88386247f8abab11b27cceddb6b2ea6731e0ed","tid":1787980,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:05:36.000Z","msg":"你都唔係放開巴士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"我係"},{"pid":"c453d5e9afd597ad221608ec07128bafca309aa7","tid":1787980,"uid":135461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:05:47.000Z","msg":"再講會點？你會放針？"},{"pid":"1c2b62aeefdd6539b59a62a1d4b62bd4414fae91","tid":1787980,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"放黨鐵未"},{"pid":"f78402aa1a1ce7e2b6d6878706e78cbbbdea8ab8","tid":1787980,"uid":321674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T10:06:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64129f67caba70dc03fde62305acb209e4f56594","tid":1787980,"uid":217641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201